{"tid":1908560,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"擔心紙鈔有武漢肺炎病毒殘留　大媽用微波爐消毒紙鈔被燒焦","createTime":"2020-03-03T11:09:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-03T11:56:48.000Z","uid":28114,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"63177590bd35b4c789bee3d9be0b7753d92887b9","tid":1908560,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T11:09:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2580000/2580162/money_thumb_20200303_S_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2580000%2F2580162%2Fmoney_thumb_20200303_S_600.jpg&h=5e57b995&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 內地大媽擔心紙鈔有病毒殘留，用微波爐加熱消毒，最終燒焦紙鈔。<br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎（武漢肺炎）疫情持續，市民開始養成勤消毒的習慣，加強清潔手機、鑰匙等用品，以免沾上細菌或病毒。江蘇無錫一名大媽擔心人民幣上可能沾染新冠肺炎病毒，將3千元現金放入微波爐中加熱消毒，最終全部燒焦！<br />\n<br />\n婦人將3千元鈔票放入微波爐「消毒」<br />\n<br />\n由新冠肺炎爆發開始，不少人都擔心病毒會經不同途徑傳播，例如紙鈔及硬幣等每日流通性極高的物品。綜合內地傳媒報導，江蘇無錫江陰市一名李姓婦人，2月底擔心銀紙上沾染「新冠肺炎病毒」，於是將3,125元人民幣（約3,484港元）鈔票放入微波爐加熱消毒。「叮錢」不到一分鐘，微波爐就飄出了「燶」味。李婦急忙取出現金，但大部分鈔票已經燒焦，碳化至黑色。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2580162/?r=mcsdfb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2580162%2F%3Fr%3Dmcsdfb&d=HqwfJ7ndl2RLmQbQQ2LVpi8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=f88acd5e\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2580162/?r=mcsdfb</a>"},{"pid":"42f2ebef6347bfb497eca0ddd0949a13dd9529cc","tid":1908560,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T11:10:27.000Z","msg":"銀行職員逐張檢查　最終換上嶄新鈔票<br />\n<br />\n李婦大為心痛，帶著鈔票到中信銀行江陰支行求助。由於紙幣被燒焦，難以用儀器辨別，獲銀行職員逐張仔細揭開檢查、鑑定及點算，最終為她換上新鈔票。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2580000/2580162/654b47daly1gcgr3kzt39j20u0140npe_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2580000%2F2580162%2F654b47daly1gcgr3kzt39j20u0140npe_600.jpg&h=84daddac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 銀行職員為婦人逐一點算燒焦的紙幣。<br />\n<br />\n銀行方面透露，在防疫敏感時期，金融機構每日將鈔票入庫前，都會為鈔票噴消毒液及用紫外光燈消毒最少1小時，存放14天以上再投放市場，因此從金融機構出來的都是「乾淨錢」，可放心使用。不過當地仍是鼓勵民眾盡量使用電子錢包及信月卡等方式付款，減低疫情傳播風險。<br />\n<br />\n網民：真的太沒常識！<br />\n<br />\n事件引起網民熱議，有網民直言沒常識，「家裡用消毒水噴噴就好了呀，真的太沒常識啦！還好人沒事」、「太可惜了，真是讓人哭笑不得呀，有點心疼」；有網民稱幸虧到最後銀行肯更換鈔票，否則就蝕錢了，「這得多心疼啊，幸虧銀行好心，給兌換了」；另有網民提醒，「摸完錢幣後好好洗手問題應該不大，而不是做這麼無語的舉動。」"},{"pid":"30f53071d0636f6fef477aa7d8c87e8bc83f4025","tid":1908560,"uid":201414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T11:11:10.000Z","msg":"擔心啲銀紙有病毒 俾曬啲銀紙我洗咪唔驚囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"579e0f46df2a2b4ec89b5e3777f2a379afc0de8d","tid":1908560,"uid":42188,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T11:12:00.000Z","msg":"燒毛主席個肖像，仲唔拎去打靶？"},{"pid":"f43defd6f3e3c14b6da3c8fc48741001962b96cb","tid":1908560,"uid":4574,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T11:13:21.000Z","msg":"個微波爐<br />\n都唔撚駛要"},{"pid":"0690f31d8ae07b6220007e2adfe8dd186dcd6c4d","tid":1908560,"uid":39871,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T11:14:13.000Z","msg":"火燒毛魔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n顛覆國家政權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bdc1fde15159d3e4ebff235d4562d91416ad3c8","tid":1908560,"uid":58147,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T11:15:15.000Z","msg":"好似未見過呢款100蚊紙。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"243e6cc6ac9204c1dc2645f5822ef5b78b077755","tid":1908560,"uid":37733,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T11:15:15.000Z","msg":"唔識就好心用一張細銀紙試下先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"174ca572d9a2c1baf9710c3e3ab0d5db3c39611a","tid":1908560,"uid":49955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T11:15:48.000Z","msg":"抗通漲微波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd7cdabdeb15267b57a2583cf1c484876dcc6764","tid":1908560,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T11:39:58.000Z","msg":"CLS <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"509d534b747cf32984ada133f6821e49614be6ea","tid":1908560,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T11:56:48.000Z","msg":"又話支那cashless好先進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}